  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "3554217a46b0be7b4f00d616372305ea3c37ce6bc28bb59c1636d87869c66fd5": "You come to speak to me, [?]?",
    "6f2a07767c444b8224d67c8cc8ae925f72a567898c11f28e8da9c75f335460d1": "Big thanks, [?]. When Colony safe, Herman reward you good.",
    "75e37ef4864d714cabcc62a726a10169aa0a1e14c87cba79354b5f1f10ad5cd3": "So, [?]! I did hear from Herr Caranos that you were to our Colony coming. The Director in his office is waiting for you.",
    "76c51c2707f1261a241fac916d6270a509aeb2da7f040639f8c89b7160e5dd70": "[?]! I hear you fetch mighty army for us!",
    "aecff5f5b67699f1a43b4deb18ede143b75c097e0509e16d94813415956af4ad": "Ah, lovely fresh monkfish straight from the sea! Now you bring me [?] more, ja?",
    "b9203e1d894d68b82d9cb6d5592695898eac2d064363242a7222a60ba7ce5acf": "This is superb, [?]! Now I store these carefully, and you go help little Frankie.",
    "bc7c545e95c02e1e87f56a948c6ff9add21ca13c347263d446293da2b9a69e88": "Thanks [?]!",
    "dcc7c9dad4cfc5fa3b5dab3f9287ef523436e5a9121168319565026f211391e9": "This is superb, [?]! Now I store these carefully, and you go tell Herr Caranos.",
    "eb455791cfd26a9cc8e4e63b07ca9560ba7d326dca6670dfbf98a9d3900da404": "It good to see you, [?], but many things I have to do with lovely fresh monkfish you bring me earlier."
  }
